data.description:
Beautiful single-story home in Georgetown's sought after Westhaven neighborhood. Spacious, open floor plan with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and no neighbors behind. The dining space and living area are bright and open making it ideal for entertaining. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, tile backsplash and a huge walk in pantry. The primary bedroom offers a large bathroom with large walk-in shower and spacious walk-in closet. Meticulously maintained, this home offer abundant upgrades- sink and faucet, Light fixtures in entry and dining room. 10 min to Downtown Georgetown and Round Rock Outlet Mall . REFRIGERATOR, WASHER AND DRYER INCLUDED.

Owner pays HOA dues. Tenant pays for the utilities. No smoking inside the house.
